<?php $labels=['draft'=>'Draft','counting'=>'Sedang dihitung','review'=>'Ditinjau','completed'=>'Selesai','cancelled'=>'Dibatalkan'];?><header class="page-head"><div><a class="eyebrow" href="<?=url('/admin/stock-opnames')?>">← Kembali ke daftar opname</a><h1>Hitung stok fisik</h1><p><?=e($opname['opname_number'])?> · <?=count($items)?> item</p></div><span class="badge"><?=e($labels[$opname['status']]??$opname['status'])?></span></header><form method="post" action="<?=url('/admin/stock-opnames/'.$opname['id'].'/complete')?>" onsubmit="return confirm('Selesaikan stock opname? Stok sistem akan dikoreksi mengikuti jumlah fisik dan sesi tidak dapat diedit lagi.')"><?=csrf_field()?><section class="panel"><p class="panel-help">Masukkan jumlah fisik setiap produk. Periksa kembali semua nilai sebelum menyelesaikan opname.</p><div class="table-wrap" tabindex="0" aria-label="Item stock opname, geser horizontal bila diperlukan"><table><thead><tr><th>Produk</th><th>SKU</th><th>Stok sistem</th><th>Stok fisik</th></tr></thead><tbody><?php foreach($items as $x):?><tr><td><?=e($x['product_name'].' · '.$x['variant_name'])?></td><td><?=e($x['sku'])?></td><td><?=$x['system_qty']?></td><td><label><span class="sr-only">Stok fisik <?=e($x['product_name'].' '.$x['variant_name'])?></span><input class="qty-input" type="number" min="0" name="physical[<?=$x['id']?>]" value="<?=e($x['physical_qty']??$x['system_qty'])?>" <?=$opname['status']==='completed'?'disabled':''?>></label></td></tr><?php endforeach?></tbody></table></div></section><?php if($opname['status']!=='completed'):?><div class="final-action"><button class="button button-large">Selesaikan dan koreksi stok</button><small>Tindakan ini tidak dapat dibatalkan.</small></div><?php endif?></form>
